data.title: Dutch lunch
data.text: One of Pueblo's great little delis. Order a dutch lunch and custom loafs of bread. The sweetrolls are very delicious. This is the place to order your lunch trays for any occassion.

data.title: Grocery Shopping
data.text: Looking for homemade goodies? Want AWESOME cold cuts? Delicious pasta? Fresh baked breads? Cinnamon buns the size of your child's head? All served with a smile and the feel of visiting an old friend? Go to Zoelsmann's! But get there early! The best breads sell out early! Call ahead and place an order...or have them cater your luncheons! You won't be disappointed!
